#
# Environment Configuration File
#
# This file stores sensitive configuration values and external service
# credentials used by the Karaoke system backend.
#
# Responsibilities:
# - Define API keys and service endpoints
# - Configure Supabase connection (URL + public anon key)
# - Provide optional integrations (YouTube API, mobile queue URL)
#
# Variables:
# - YOUTUBE_API_KEY: Used for searching songs via YouTube Data API
# - SUPABASE_URL: Base URL of the Supabase project
# - SUPABASE_ANON_KEY: Public API key for Supabase access
# - MOBILE_QUEUE_URL: Endpoint for mobile queue interface
#
# Security Notes:
# - DO NOT commit this file to version control (add to .gitignore)
# - Never expose API keys in frontend/client-side code
# - Rotate keys immediately if they are leaked
#
# Usage:
# Loaded via python-dotenv or environment variables in deployment

